   - `JWT_SECRET_KEY` - Strong secret key (64+ characters)
   - `SUPER_ADMIN_PASSWORD` - Secure admin password
   - `EMAIL_PASSWORD` - Email service password
   - `REDIS_PASSWORD` - Redis password
   - API keys for threat intelligence services

